txt.en: You have encountered the malevolent Skorneval. Barely under Drugât's command, this Ruthless Dead terrorizes any of the living in Ringló Vale.
Skorneval can be found patrolling Ringló Vale.\n\nYou have encountered Skorneval and should defeat him for the good of the people in Ringló Vale.
You have defeated Skorneval and his warband.
